Achievements.Name: Silver Medalist
Achievements.Description: Reach silver time in 10 levels.

Achievements.Name: Silver Collector
Achievements.Description: Reach silver time in 25 levels.

Achievements.Name: Silver Champion
Achievements.Description: Reach silver time in all levels.

Achievements.Name: Gold Medalist
Achievements.Description: Reach gold time in 5 levels.

Achievements.Name: Gold Collector
Achievements.Description: Reach gold time in 10 levels.

Achievements.Name: Gold Hoarder
Achievements.Description: Reach gold time in 25 levels.

Achievements.Name: Swimming in Gold
Achievements.Description: Reach gold time in all levels.

Achievements.Name: Ball Conservationist
Achievements.Description: Clear all levels without losing any balls (multiballs dont count).

Achievements.Name: Leaf Blower
Achievements.Description: Clear all levels in the Forest area.

Achievements.Name: Zen Exploder
Achievements.Description: Clear all levels in the Garden area.

Achievements.Name: Sand Blaster
Achievements.Description: Clear all levels in the Desert area.

Achievements.Name: Dive Bomber
Achievements.Description: Clear all levels in the Underwater area.

Achievements.Name: Space Destroyer
Achievements.Description: Clear all levels in the Space area.

Achievements.Name: Knower of the Secret
Achievements.Description: Unlock the secret level by clearing all other levels.

Achievements.Name: Black Belt Cube Slicer
Achievements.Description: Reach a score of 1,500 in the secret level (#55).

Achievements.Name: Unlocking 101
Achievements.Description: Earn enough stars to unlock the Garden area.

Achievements.Name: Cube Hitter
Achievements.Description: Hit 5,000 cubes (fireballs dont count).

Achievements.Name: Cube Champion
Achievements.Description: Hit 20,000 cubes (fireballs dont count).

Achievements.Name: Cubonator
Achievements.Description: Hit 100,000 cubes (fireballs dont count).

Achievements.Name: Pyrotechnician
Achievements.Description: Blow up 5,000 other cubes by using explosive cubes.

Achievements.Name: Multitasker
Achievements.Description: Keep at least 3 balls in play 15 seconds. Hit each ball at least once and don't lose any balls.

Achievements.Name: Left, Right, Left, Right
Achievements.Description: Hit the same ball alternately with the left and right hand 10 times without hitting any other balls.

Achievements.Name: Multiballistic
Achievements.Description: Hit at least 6 different balls without losing any balls in between.

Achievements.Name: Juggernaut
Achievements.Description: Break at least 30 cubes with a single heavy ball (explosion chain reactions dont count).
